item.title: Login Background?
item.dc:creator: @badger41 badger41
item.description:
@badger41 wrote:

for the login background it is packed into the cache, using toms cache suit you go to edit jagex archives > title > title.dat is the background, change the extension to .png and you can view it as an image.

For the interfaces, those are also packed into the cache, using toms cache suit you go to edit jagex archives > interface(s).jag > data.dat is the file that holds all the data for every interface, you will have to edit the file using peterbjornxâ€™s interface editor or lins interface editor.
